        "summary": "<b><span class=\"dtstart\"><span class=\"value\" title=\"2017-04-27\">Thursday, April 27, 2017</span> (<span\tclass=\"value\"\ttitle=\"15:15:00\">3:15 PM</span></span> - <span class=\"dtend\"\ttitle=\"15:45:00\">3:45 PM</span>)</b> <div>Location: <span class=\"location\">Center for Student Wellbeing</span></div> <div class=\"description\"><p>Join us in the Center for Student Wellbeing for silent meditation practice.&nbsp; With practice, meditation helps to quiet the mind, build resiliency, and reduce stress.</p></div>",
