        "time": "17:00:00",
        "date": "2017-04-27",
        "text": "<b><span class=\"dtstart\"><span class=\"value\" title=\"2017-04-27\">Thursday, April 27, 2017</span> (<span\tclass=\"value\"\ttitle=\"17:00:00\">5:00 PM</span></span> - <span class=\"dtend\"\ttitle=\"18:00:00\">6:00 PM</span>)</b> <div>Location: <span class=\"location\">Center for Student Wellbeing </span></div> <div class=\"description\"><p>Project Safe is excited to give you a sneak peak of our Yoga for Trauma Survivors program. In collaboration with the Center for Student Wellbeing, Project Safe will be offering a 1 hour program for Survivors of Trauma. The first half will be an informative session about the ways trauma impacts the body and the benefits of yoga practice. The second half will be an opportunity for students to practice newly learned skills. Students of all levels are welcome to join.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>",
