        "title": "OIG: Journal Club on Injury Prevention in Sports Medicine",
        "summary": "<b><span class=\"dtstart\"><span class=\"value\" title=\"2017-05-16\">Tuesday, May 16, 2017</span> (<span\tclass=\"value\"\ttitle=\"18:00:00\">6:00 PM</span></span> - <span class=\"dtend\"\ttitle=\"19:00:00\">7:00 PM</span>)</b> <div>Location: <span class=\"location\">411 A-B-C</span></div> <div class=\"description\"><p>Join us for a presentation by Dr. Alex Diamond as he discusses Injury Prevention in Sports Medicine!</p></div>",
