        "summary": "<b><span class=\"dtstart\"><span class=\"value\" title=\"2017-06-12\">Monday, June 12, 2017</span> (<span\tclass=\"value\"\ttitle=\"12:00:00\">12:00 PM</span></span> - <span class=\"dtend\"\ttitle=\"13:00:00\">1:00 PM</span>)</b> <div>Location: <span class=\"location\">208 Light Hall</span></div> <div class=\"description\"><p>Lecture</p></div>",
